           move      23                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Linea 24                                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      24                   to   v-lin                  .
