      *                  * Altrimenti : reimpostazione                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cnf-imp-100.
       acc-cnf-imp-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Cancellazione prompts                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Linea 23                                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      23                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
