      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se oltre ultima riga da visualizzare       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    not  > w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                     go to vis-cor-reg-200.
       vis-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
