      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           inspect   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa
                                     replacing all " " by   "-"       .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
      *
           move      w-lin-pri-lin-vid    to   v-lin                  .
           add       w-lin-num-lin-vis    to   v-lin                  .
      *
           move      36                   to   v-pos                  .
