      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Specifica libera                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-rig-spc-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      22                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rig-spc-lib        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-rig-spc-999.
           exit.

